Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也提起精神来做早操吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，先从腕部运动开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，丝茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不用做了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，早安ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，吵醒你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在晒榻榻米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大扫除啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们经常受您的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公寓里大扫除的工作\N不也需要男人帮忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌弃的话\N请尽量派工作给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，加油
