Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，发现灰尘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现灰尘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里，就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，这里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样做，知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，那来扫除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，要掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，接下来要擦外面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ留在這裡看著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，你还好吧？
