Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这辈子最大的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…\N我找到適合ちぃ的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能让她穿穿看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以，谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，ちぃ\N妳能到我房裡來一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别给日比谷小姐添麻烦喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该差不多了吧
