Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能穿穿看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是通往屋顶的门吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是说这是仓库？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我换好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然很合身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这原本就是你的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ的衣服？
